hot 5.png", "id": "2798915413752699", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982699_2798915417086032_7172758115676658381_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xVb5IZJ_SakQ7kNvgF9cEyP&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDWHpXIVvevr6FLT94U7oaTBddz2CVApQ5S_J6O5o6MGw&oe=67444FCD"}, {"file_name": "EF-VR App Screenshot 7.png", "id": "156438259646824", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974453_156438262980157_1627242679791238025_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4BdMuAwFfFIQ7kNvgGC8lmj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAo5VNRegkkOsDGxq0rqD2_08q-lJcJykTegIz5YlCfUQ&oe=67446E6B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "EF-VR Oculus App Lab Cover Art Landscape.png", "id": "252965883002072", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035424_252965886335405_7319811021161173829_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=CCAaZ4LGq1IQ7kNvgG7abBX&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBgu7NpYjVd3mMuq_QqVSWKDNRgQCzE8_GmO58IJKLwFA&oe=6744519D"}, "display_name": "Edge Factor VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Edge Factor's Virtual Reality Experiences are all about experiential learning. VR takes this to the next level, giving students a closer look at interests and industries during their career exploration.\n\nLearn about industries from around the country. Experience tours and demonstrations with industry professionals. Interact with objects, inspect life-size models, and discover a whole new way to learn. Explore gamified experiences with quizzes, challenges, and experimentation to ignite a passion for learning and career exploration.\n\nVirtual Reality  =  High Impact Experiential Learning\n\nAn existing Edge Factor membership is required to access.", "short_description": "Take experiential learning to the next level with Edge Factor's Virtual Reality Experience. Explore industries from around the